<hr><a name="_details"></a><h2>Detailed Description</h2>
The button widget consists of an elevated area with a caption. 
<p>
If the user clicks on the elevated area it will be sunken and generate an event when it is released. When the button has focus it will display transparent borders.<hr><h2>Function Documentation</h2>
